# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cloudflare Pages — _redirects
# Format: [source] [destination] [status] [!force]
#
# NOTE: www → non-www is handled here as a fallback.
# For production, also configure Custom Domains in the
# Cloudflare Pages dashboard: set ghaidak.com as primary,
# www as alias → it auto-redirects without needing this file.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Redirect www → apex (301 permanent, ! forces even if file exists)
https://www.ghaidak.com/* https://ghaidak.com/:splat 301

# HTTP → HTTPS (Cloudflare handles this via Always Use HTTPS,
# but belt-and-suspenders for proxy edge cases)
http://ghaidak.com/*     https://ghaidak.com/:splat 301!
http://www.ghaidak.com/* https://ghaidak.com/:splat 301!
